Install everything
--------------------
Windows: not supported

Linux:
  $ bash install.sh

Bash
--------------------
Windows: n/a

Linux:
  $ cd bash
  $ sudo bash install.sh

Vim
--------------------
Windows:
  c:\settings>cd vim
  c:\settings>install.bat

Linux:
  $ cd vim
  $ sudo bash install.sh

Support
--------------------
Installing the Monaco font

  Windows:
    Right click support/fonts/Monaco.ttf -> Install

  Linux: (tested on ubuntu 10.04, 10.10, 11.04)
    $ cd support
    $ sudo bash install-fonts.sh
